{
  "Specific Heat and Calorimetry": "特定热量和热量测量",
  "This lesson covers the fundamental measures of center used to analyze and summarize data sets. You'll learn how to calculate and apply the mean, median, and mode, and understand when each is most appropriate.": "这个课程涵盖了分析和总结数据集的中心的基本测量方法。 您将学会如何计算和应用平均值、 中位数和模式, 并了解何时最合适 。",
  "What is 'specific heat capacity'?": "什么是“特定热能”?",
  "Specific heat capacity c appears in Q = mc(Delta T). Materials with high c resist temperature changes; those with low c change temperature easily.": "特定热能c出现在 Q = mc (Delta T)中。 高 c 抗温变化的材料; 低 c 变化温度的材料。",
  "What is 'calorimetry'?": "什么是“量测”?",
  "Calorimetry measures heat transfer during processes. It uses the principle that in an isolated system, total heat exchange is zero.": "它采用的原则是,在一个孤立的系统中,总热交换为零。",
  "What is 'latent heat'?": "什么是\"冷热\"?",
  "Latent heat (Q = mL) is 'hidden' heat that changes the phase of a substance without changing its temperature.": "中热(Q = mL)是“隐藏”热,可以改变物质的阶段,而不会改变温度。",
  "What is 'latent heat of fusion'?": "什么是“冷热聚变”?",
  "Latent heat of fusion L_f is the energy per kg for the solid-liquid phase transition. For water, L_f = 334,000 J/kg.": "L_f聚变的热量是固体-液体阶段过渡的每公斤能量。对于水,L_f = 334,000 J/kg。",
  "What is 'latent heat of vaporization'?": "什么是“蒸发的冷热”?",
  "Latent heat of vaporization L_v is the energy per kg for the liquid-gas transition. For water, L_v = 2.26 x 10^6 J/kg.": "蒸发液态L_v的热量是液态气体转换的每公斤能量。对于水,L_v = 2.26 x 10.6 J/kg。",
  "What is a 'calorimeter'?": "什么是“计算仪”?",
  "A calorimeter is an insulated container that minimizes heat exchange with the environment, enabling accurate measurement of heat transfers.": "热量计是一种隔热容器,能最大限度地减少与环境的热交换,从而能够准确测量热转移。",
  "What is 'heat capacity'?": "什么是“热能”?",
  "Heat capacity C = mc is the product of mass and specific heat. It represents the heat needed to raise the entire object by 1 K.": "热能C = mc 是质量和特定热量的产物,代表将整个物体提高1K所需的热量。",
  "What is 'phase transition'?": "什么是“分阶段过渡”?",
  "Phase transitions (melting, boiling, sublimation, etc.) occur at specific temperatures where energy goes into changing intermolecular bonding rather than temperature.": "阶段过渡(熔炼、沸腾、升华等)发生在特定温度下,在这种温度下,能量会演变成分子间联,而不是温度。",
  "What is 'thermal equilibrium' in the context of calorimetry?": "“热平衡”在热量测量方面是什么?",
  "In calorimetry, thermal equilibrium is the final state. The equilibrium temperature is found by setting Q_lost + Q_gained = 0.": "在热量测量中,热平衡是最终状态。平衡温度通过设置  lost + gained = 0 来找到。",
  "What is 'molar heat capacity'?": "什么是\"月热能力\"?",
  "Molar heat capacity C_m = Mc where M is molar mass. For ideal monatomic gases, C_v = (3/2)R and C_p = (5/2)R.": "摩尔热能 C_m = Mc M是摩尔质量。对于理想的单质气体,C_v = (3/2)R 和 C_p = (5/2)R 。",
  "A 200 g copper block (c = 385 J/(kg*C)) at 300 C is dropped into 500 g of water (c = 4186 J/(kg*C)) at 20 C. What is the equilibrium temperature?": "300C时的200克铜块(c=385焦耳/(kg*C))在20C时跌至500克水(c=4186焦耳/(kg*C))中。 平衡温度是多少?",
  "0.2(385)(300-T) = 0.5(4186)(T-20). 77(300-T) = 2093(T-20). 23100 - 77T = 2093T - 41860. 64960 = 2170T. T = 29.9 C.": "0.2(385)(300-T)=0.5(4186)(T-20)。 77(300-T)=2093(T-20)。 23100-77T=2093T-41860。 64960=2170T。T=29.9C。",
  "50 g of ice at 0 C is added to 200 g of water at 70 C in an insulated cup. Is all the ice melted, and what is the final temperature?": "在隔热杯中,0.C时的50克冰加到200克水中,70克。所有的冰都融化了,最后温度是多少?",
  "Heat available = 0.2(4186)(70) = 58604 J. Heat to melt ice = 0.05(334000) = 16700 J. Remaining = 41904 J. Then 0.05(4186)(T) + 0.2(4186)(T-70) + 16700 = 0 gives T = 41.3 C.": "热可用= 02(4186)(70) = 58604 J. 熔冰热= 0.05 (33400) = 16700 J. 剩余= 41904 J. 然后 0.05 (4186)(T) + 0.2(4186)(T-70) + 16700 = 0 give T = 41.3 C.",
  "A calorimeter contains 100 g of water at 25 C. A 50 g metal sample at 100 C is added and the equilibrium temperature is 30 C. What is the specific heat of the metal?": "热量计中含水100克,温度为25C。 添加50克金属样本,温度为100C,平衡温度为30C。 金属的具体热量是多少?",
  "0.05(c)(100-30) = 0.1(4186)(30-25). 3.5c = 2093. c = 598 J/(kg*C).": "0.05(c)(100-30) = 0.1(4186)(30-25) 3.5c = 2093.c = 598 J/(千克*C)。",
  "In an experiment, 10 g of steam at 100 C is passed into 200 g of water at 20 C. What is the final temperature? (L_v = 2260 J/g, c_water = 4.186 J/(g*C))": "在一次实验中,10克蒸汽在100°C时通过,在20°C时达到200克水。 最后温度是多少? (L_v = 2260 J/g, c_water = 4.186 J/(g*C))",
  "Steam condenses: 10(2260) = 22600 J released. Then 10(4.186)(100-T) + 200(4.186)(T-20) = 22600. Solving: T = 46.8 C.": "蒸汽浓缩:10(2260) = 22600 J 释放。然后10(4.186)(100-T) + 200(4.186)(T-20) = 22600。溶剂:T = 46.8 C。",
  "A 1 kg lead bullet (c = 128 J/(kg*C)) traveling at 400 m/s strikes a target and stops. If 50% of the kinetic energy heats the bullet, what is its temperature rise?": "1公斤铅子弹(c = 128 J/(kg*C))以400米/秒/秒的航程打击目标并停止。 如果50%的动能能给子弹加热,它的温度上升是多少?",
  "KE = 0.5(1)(400^2) = 80000 J. 50% = 40000 J heats bullet. Delta T = Q/(mc) = 40000/(1*128) = 312.5 C. Wait, let me recalculate: 0.5*1*160000 = 80000. 50% of 80000 = 40000. Delta T = 40000/128 = 312.5 C. The answer of 625 C corresponds to 100% conversion; with 50%, it's 312 C.": "KE = 0.5(1)(4000.002) = 80000 J.50% = 40000 J热子弹。Delta T = Q/(mc) = 40000/(1*128) = 312.5 C. 等等,让我重新计算: 0.5*1*160000 = 80000. 50% 80000 = 40000. Delta T = 40000/128 = 312.5 C. 625 C 的回答相当于 100%的转换; 50%为 312 C.",
  "A chemistry student mixes 100 mL of 1 M HCl with 100 mL of 1 M NaOH in a calorimeter. The temperature rises 6.8 C. What is the enthalpy of neutralization per mole? (Assume density = 1 g/mL, c = 4.186 J/(g*C))": "化学学生在卡路里计,化学学生混合了100毫升(1毫升1毫升)和100毫升(1毫升1毫升)。 温度上升6.8 C. 每一摩尔的中和性吗? (表示密度=1克/毫升,c=4.186 J/(g*C))",
  "Q = mc(Delta T) = 200(4.186)(6.8) = 5693 J. Moles reacted = 0.1 mol. Enthalpy = -5693/0.1 = -56930 J/mol = -56.9 kJ/mol.": "Q = mc (Delta T) = 200(4.186)(6.8) = 5693 J. Moles反应 = 0.1 mol. Enthalpy =-5693/0.1 = - 56930 J/mol = - 569. kJ/mol。",
  "A student measures the specific heat of an unknown metal using a calorimeter. Three trials give values of 450, 460, and 440 J/(kg*C). The accepted value for the metal is 449 J/(kg*C). What is the percent error of the average?": "学生用卡路里计量未知金属的具体热量。三次试验给出了450、460和440 J/(千克*C)的值。该金属的公认值为449 J/(千克*C)。平均值的百分率误差是多少?",
  "Average = (450+460+440)/3 = 450 J/(kg*C). Percent error = |450-449|/449 * 100 = 0.22%. Approximately 0.07% considering rounding.": "平均 = (450+460+440)/3 = 450 J/(千克*C),误差 = 450-449 /449 * 100 = 0.22%,考虑到四舍五入,约0.07%。"
}